# AI-Evaluation-Portfolio
This repository collects my exercises and experiments in AI Evaluation and Red Teaming. It's a working portfolio so it will change and grow as I explore new tools and methodologies rather than serving as a static showcase.

My background is in Quality Assurance so I would expect deviations from any kind of standard in AI Eval to fall in that direction.

